{"tid":1714190,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"當年有個行政長官又係個大仆街黎","createTime":"2019-11-13T00:08:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T01:28:35.000Z","uid":33359,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6e9ae1d67112f0a913d6725db01e4e08994333b0","tid":1714190,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:08:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/44/Chen_Yi.jpg/200px-Chen_Yi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2F4%2F44%2FChen_Yi.jpg%2F200px-Chen_Yi.jpg&h=3901e988&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n引發台灣228事件及其後38年既白色恐怖<br />\n死超過數萬人"},{"pid":"111e77d24c7e1c12d1527c5658ae2e468c7fde0e","tid":1714190,"uid":152944,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:09:17.000Z","msg":"竟然唔係定仔"},{"pid":"13ced78774b03e2f5296b371e5dafa5186a0fd59","tid":1714190,"uid":278228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:09:35.000Z","msg":"借po一個位<br />\n大家好，示威其實都4個月<br />\n我地每次行動都會影響到民生，<br />\n琴日我係沙田去暴大，<br />\n沿途好多街彷屌road block，又話過分乜乜77<br />\n但冇人提過黑警好似殺人咁攻中大<br />\n因為呢件事<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔關佢事</span></strong></span><br />\n每次咁辛苦做咁多野，到頭嚟都係要比人屌<br />\n既然係咁，<br />\n大家係咪時候諗下要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">直搗皇龍</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n唔關政見問題，係有的確為所不少既人只關注生計<br />\n同有冇屋企番，甚至會主動清road block<br />\n即使唔係撐警<br />\n既然守中大又要送頭，守旺角又要通頂<br />\n但係都迫唔到政府做啲乜<br />\n<br />\n4個月喇<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>點解宜家仲唔升級去搞啲官</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n至少仲會多人支持<br />\n<br />\n策略：小隊突擊，人在明我在暗"},{"pid":"e5c877fd59fb5c54d473cab06adfd804e25b972a","tid":1714190,"uid":52073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T01:17:42.000Z","msg":"g持"},{"pid":"36243e583a9373358be53abc62462bf9a2aa2021","tid":1714190,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T01:20:10.000Z","msg":"咁熟口面"},{"pid":"38bb0066c7d9a4bc2ebe2fb70f6d14e0f657aff4","tid":1714190,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"36243e583a9373358be53abc62462bf9a2aa2021","tid":1714190,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T01:20:10.000Z","msg":"咁熟口面"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T01:28:35.000Z","msg":"台灣省行政長官 陳儀"}]}